# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OSOWOSO Website Build System
# web-create / web-deploy — configuration
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Website
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#TITLE='My Website'

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GoatCounter analytics
# Sing up or host your own https://www.goatcounter.com
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#GOATCOUNTER_URL="https://yoursite.goatcounter.com/count"

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Giscus comments
# Get these values from https://giscus.app
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#GISCUS_REPO="user/repo"
#GISCUS_REPO_ID="R_xxxxxxxxxx"
#GISCUS_CATEGORY="Comments"
#GISCUS_CATEGORY_ID="DIC_xxxxxxxxxx"

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Git forge override — set if auto-detection fails
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#FORGE_URL="https://git.example.com"

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Deployment (optional)
# Other directories (repositories) using this template
# Updated by web-deploy script
#
# LIST entry format (pipe-separated):
#	"path|TITLE|GISCUS_REPO|GISCUS_REPO_ID|GISCUS_CATEGORY|GISCUS_CATEGORY_ID"
#
# Empty fields fall back to shared values above.
# TITLE falls back to dirname.
# GISCUS_REPO is auto-detected from git remote if empty.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#DIR="$HOME/git"

#LIST=(
#	"$DIR/myrepo||||||"
#	"$DIR/otherrepo|Other Repo|||||"
#	"$DIR/customrepo|Custom|user/customrepo|R_custom|Announcements|DIC_custom"
#)
